1
00:01:10,090 --> 00:01:13,204
Madame Manfah, queen of dark magic.

2
00:01:13,204 --> 00:01:16,433
I want you to cast a curse on these people.

3
00:01:16,433 --> 00:01:17,896
Those two are on our side, Madam!

4
00:01:17,896 --> 00:01:19,683
They’re not on our side anymore.

5
00:01:19,683 --> 00:01:21,076
I had neck pain all night out of nowhere.

6
00:01:21,076 --> 00:01:22,380
I’ve got back pain too.

7
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:24,163
I think we’ve just been working too hard.

8
00:01:24,163 --> 00:01:25,663
I'm having such a great time with you, Ploy.

9
00:01:27,153 --> 00:01:28,901
Want a piece of custard? It’s really good.

10
00:01:28,901 --> 00:01:30,367
Everyone looks a bit strange.

11
00:01:30,367 --> 00:01:32,038
Like you’re under a spell.

12
00:01:32,038 --> 00:01:34,945
Since I’m here, I might as well go all out.

13
00:01:34,945 --> 00:01:36,945
Just one night, and they’ll all be finished.

14
00:01:37,575 --> 00:01:39,575
It’s begun...Madame Manfah.

15
00:01:44,568 --> 00:01:52,568
Madam Porn, I’m sorry we messed up with, umm…

16
00:01:52,955 --> 00:01:53,821
Just say it.

17
00:01:53,821 --> 00:01:56,328
Come on, speak up.
If one of us is in trouble, we’re all in trouble together.

18
00:01:56,328 --> 00:01:57,040
Right, Madam?

19
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,240
Hey.

20
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,350
Hey.

21
00:01:58,501 --> 00:02:00,332
Wait, what…

22
00:02:00,332 --> 00:02:01,404
Madam’s been here the whole time.

23
00:02:01,404 --> 00:02:02,238
Then who’s that?

24
00:02:02,238 --> 00:02:03,238
Siri.

25
00:02:05,155 --> 00:02:07,581
Oh, Madam, you’re here.

26
00:02:08,143 --> 00:02:09,854
And what are these two doing here?

27
00:02:09,854 --> 00:02:10,924
Nothing.

28
00:02:10,924 --> 00:02:14,924
All-New and Kreetha came to apologize for messing up their job.

29
00:02:15,267 --> 00:02:16,700
So, should we finish them off now, Madam?

30
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:19,805
Hey, Siri. For something this small,
do you really need to kill us?

31
00:02:19,805 --> 00:02:23,806
I meant the documents. Should we just file them away, Madam?
They’re piling up everywhere.

32
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:27,919
Oh, you scared me.
I thought Madam was mad at us.

33
00:02:28,187 --> 00:02:30,294
Come on.
Go do what I told you to.

34
00:02:30,294 --> 00:02:31,294
Yes.

35
00:02:34,962 --> 00:02:38,555
About your mistake, I understand.

36
00:02:38,555 --> 00:02:41,347
I should be the one to apologize to you.

37
00:02:41,347 --> 00:02:42,449
For what, Madam?

38
00:02:42,449 --> 00:02:46,449
For sending you out risking your lives for me.

39
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:50,480
I know everyone treasures their own life, right?

40
00:02:51,666 --> 00:02:54,899
Then thank you so much, Madam, for understanding us.

41
00:02:54,899 --> 00:02:56,454
Go on, get back to work.

42
00:02:56,454 --> 00:02:58,454
I’ve got things to take care of too. Go.

43
00:03:00,882 --> 00:03:01,882
Thank you so much.

44
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:10,339
How’s the task I gave you?

45
00:03:10,339 --> 00:03:11,339
All done, Madam.

46
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:15,474
But… what do you need the date, month, year, and zodiac signs of...

47
00:03:15,474 --> 00:03:18,311
Glamorous Airline crewmembers for?

48
00:03:18,311 --> 00:03:22,312
Well, I just came up with something fun.

49
00:03:22,817 --> 00:03:23,817
What are you planning, Madam?

50
00:03:35,962 --> 00:03:37,962
Guess you’ve been watching way too many dramas lately.

51
00:03:46,354 --> 00:03:49,748
Madam, where did you meet that shaman?

52
00:03:49,748 --> 00:03:50,857
That’s a secret.

53
00:03:50,857 --> 00:03:54,289
Does black magic really exist, Madam?

54
00:03:54,289 --> 00:03:56,605
You want to know, Siri?

55
00:03:56,605 --> 00:03:57,605
Fine.

56
00:04:18,636 --> 00:04:21,186
Wait, Madam. What are we even doing here?

57
00:04:21,186 --> 00:04:23,342
Last night, I watched the rerun of Khun Chai.

58
00:04:23,342 --> 00:04:26,338
The actor who played Grandmother? She was fabulous.

59
00:04:26,338 --> 00:04:27,338
Hooked on dramas again.

60
00:04:34,846 --> 00:04:35,846
Oh.

61
00:04:39,241 --> 00:04:40,707
Oh my goodness!

62
00:04:40,707 --> 00:04:43,217
Madame Shaman, Madame Shaman.

63
00:04:43,217 --> 00:04:43,932
Madame.

64
00:04:43,932 --> 00:04:44,923
I’m joking.

65
00:04:44,923 --> 00:04:46,437
Someone like me?

66
00:04:46,437 --> 00:04:48,663
Fainting over something this small?

67
00:04:48,663 --> 00:04:53,663
So this is Madame Manfah, the queen of black magic?

68
00:04:54,063 --> 00:04:55,930
She doesn’t look very convincing, Madam.

69
00:04:55,930 --> 00:04:57,558
Mhm, she’s the one.

70
00:04:57,558 --> 00:04:59,908
Tell me what you want me to do, quickly.

71
00:04:59,908 --> 00:05:04,814
Madame, I want you to cast a spell on these people.

72
00:05:04,814 --> 00:05:05,760
Siri.

73
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,760
Yes, Madam.

74
00:05:10,914 --> 00:05:12,914
Oh, that's not complete yet.

75
00:05:13,422 --> 00:05:15,536
Add photos of All-New and Kreetha too.

76
00:05:15,536 --> 00:05:17,969
Those two are on our side, Madam!

77
00:05:17,969 --> 00:05:21,517
They’re not on our side anymore.
Do as I say.

78
00:05:21,517 --> 00:05:22,517
Yes, Madam.

79
00:05:25,109 --> 00:05:27,737
Messing with dark magic is dangerous, Madam.

80
00:05:27,737 --> 00:05:29,242
Please don’t.

81
00:05:29,868 --> 00:05:32,317
This Golden Son is quite mouthy, isn’t he?

82
00:05:32,317 --> 00:05:35,381
People who keep things like this just waste offerings.

83
00:05:35,381 --> 00:05:36,573
What do you mean?

84
00:05:36,573 --> 00:05:39,877
If you want me to take this job, then give him to me.

85
00:05:39,877 --> 00:05:42,586
No! I’ll stay with Madam Porn.
No, no, no, no!

86
00:05:42,586 --> 00:05:43,586
Oh!

87
00:05:45,123 --> 00:05:46,123
I won’t go with you.

88
00:05:46,193 --> 00:05:47,141
I’ll stay with Madam Porn.

89
00:05:48,376 --> 00:05:49,376
Shut up!

90
00:05:53,281 --> 00:05:54,281
Here.

91
00:05:55,751 --> 00:05:57,817
If the you agree to take this job,

92
00:05:57,817 --> 00:06:01,527
then please ruin the lives of those six people.

93
00:06:01,527 --> 00:06:03,152
Since I came all the way here,

94
00:06:03,152 --> 00:06:04,652
I have to go all out.

95
00:06:05,742 --> 00:06:07,818
Whatever you want, Madame.

96
00:06:07,818 --> 00:06:09,450
I’ll take care of it.

97
00:06:09,450 --> 00:06:12,450
Just one night and they’ll all be finished.

98
00:06:14,523 --> 00:06:15,523
Siri, help me!

99
00:06:17,308 --> 00:06:18,308
Was that the Son's voice, Madam?

100
00:06:20,009 --> 00:06:22,317
No. I’ve raised him since he was a baby.

101
00:06:22,317 --> 00:06:25,112
I gave him red soda every day.
You can’t do this.

102
00:06:25,112 --> 00:06:27,661
No, no, no.

103
00:06:27,661 --> 00:06:30,088
Siri, Siri, it’s okay, it’s okay.

104
00:06:30,088 --> 00:06:32,596
We have to sacrifice, Siri.
We really have to.

105
00:06:32,596 --> 00:06:34,596
Cry all you want.
He’s mine now.

106
00:06:53,373 --> 00:06:55,366
It’s begun...

107
00:06:55,366 --> 00:06:56,366
Madame Manfah.

108
00:07:04,322 --> 00:07:06,514
Hey, All-New.

109
00:07:06,514 --> 00:07:09,339
You’re on the same flight as me today, right?

110
00:07:09,339 --> 00:07:10,775
Yeah.

111
00:07:10,775 --> 00:07:13,005
Why do you look so drained?

112
00:07:13,005 --> 00:07:14,717
I couldn’t sleep last night.

113
00:07:14,717 --> 00:07:17,269
Out of nowhere, my neck hurt all night.

114
00:07:17,269 --> 00:07:19,295
I tried pills, ointments, nothing worked.

115
00:07:19,295 --> 00:07:20,968
Damn, my back hurts too.

116
00:07:20,968 --> 00:07:24,642
I just saw a doctor.
He said I must’ve twisted a nerve.

117
00:07:24,642 --> 00:07:27,590
He even gave me painkillers.
It hurts like hell.

118
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:31,178
Shit. Maybe I sat at my computer too long.

119
00:07:31,178 --> 00:07:33,047
Yeah, maybe.

120
00:07:33,047 --> 00:07:36,047
Or maybe...I think we’ve just been working too hard.

121
00:07:37,601 --> 00:07:41,601
But the pain feels like...like someone’s riding on my back.

122
00:07:43,984 --> 00:07:46,219
Wait, I think I’m feeling better now.

123
00:07:46,219 --> 00:07:47,967
Want some of my pills?

124
00:07:47,967 --> 00:07:51,561
My neck hurts, and suddenly my leg does too.

125
00:07:51,561 --> 00:07:53,633
Then you should see a doctor.

126
00:07:53,633 --> 00:07:54,339
Yeah.

127
00:07:54,339 --> 00:07:55,291
There’s a clinic behind the office.

128
00:07:55,291 --> 00:07:57,291
Yeah, I should go.

129
00:07:57,877 --> 00:07:58,877
My leg...

130
00:07:59,506 --> 00:08:00,506
Why’s it so stiff?

131
00:08:02,373 --> 00:08:03,373
My neck feels so heavy.

132
00:08:04,568 --> 00:08:06,593
What the hell?

133
00:08:06,593 --> 00:08:07,593
I just went numb out of nowhere.

134
00:08:09,421 --> 00:08:10,421
What’s happening to me?

135
00:08:11,566 --> 00:08:13,513
All-New, hello?

136
00:08:13,513 --> 00:08:14,513
I...I can’t get up.

137
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:27,285
Ladies and gentlemen, passengers of Glamorous Airline,

138
00:08:27,285 --> 00:08:29,518
we have a special menu to present to you today.

139
00:08:29,518 --> 00:08:32,518
It’s Som Tum, papaya salad!

140
00:08:35,387 --> 00:08:37,612
Step right up, everyone.

141
00:08:37,612 --> 00:08:39,358
Fresh, clean,

142
00:08:39,358 --> 00:08:40,511
made to order every time.

143
00:08:40,511 --> 00:08:41,179
Super spicy.

144
00:08:41,179 --> 00:08:42,013
So tasty.

145
00:08:42,013 --> 00:08:43,803
So unbelievably spicy, everyone!

146
00:08:43,803 --> 00:08:46,914
Order first, taste first.

147
00:08:46,914 --> 00:08:50,914
We’ve got flavor powder, sparkle powder...
the more we add, the spicier it gets.

148
00:08:52,294 --> 00:08:54,807
Mixed salad, cucumber salad, we’ve got it all.

149
00:08:54,807 --> 00:08:56,242
So, what would you like?

150
00:08:56,242 --> 00:08:59,548
Thai papaya sald, Crab papaya salad, Salted egg papaya salad...

151
00:08:59,548 --> 00:09:01,296
Or maybe...me with papaya salad?

152
00:09:01,296 --> 00:09:03,800
Chai! Wolffia papaya salad!

153
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,348
I'm just entertaining the passengers.

154
00:09:05,348 --> 00:09:06,584
One Thai papaya salad, please.

155
00:09:07,171 --> 00:09:07,675
Right away!

156
00:09:07,675 --> 00:09:09,506
Since you’re our very first customer,

157
00:09:09,506 --> 00:09:10,614
both of us...

158
00:09:10,614 --> 00:09:14,615
will give you a little performance.

159
00:09:15,405 --> 00:09:16,228
Come on, let’s go.

160
00:09:16,228 --> 00:09:17,228
Here we go!

161
00:09:33,736 --> 00:09:35,088
Wow, fabulous!

162
00:09:35,088 --> 00:09:36,441
I’ll order one too.

163
00:09:36,441 --> 00:09:37,626
Coming right up!

164
00:09:37,626 --> 00:09:38,497
Alright, then.

165
00:09:38,497 --> 00:09:40,125
What kind of papaya salad would you like, ma’am?

166
00:09:40,125 --> 00:09:40,871
One Thai papaya salad, please.

167
00:09:40,871 --> 00:09:41,871
Okay.

168
00:09:42,581 --> 00:09:43,581
One Thai papaya salad.

169
00:09:44,253 --> 00:09:44,968
Alright.

170
00:09:44,968 --> 00:09:47,968
Wow, with a show like this,
shouldn't you be selling grilled chicken too?

171
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:53,749
Here it comes, chicken baked in straw, piping hot.

172
00:09:53,749 --> 00:09:57,750
The original recipe straight from Wichian Buri.

173
00:09:58,619 --> 00:09:59,651
I’ll take one!

174
00:09:59,651 --> 00:10:00,651
Of course.

175
00:10:01,881 --> 00:10:04,796
Enjoy, it’s fresh and hot.

176
00:10:04,796 --> 00:10:05,627
Would you like anything else?

177
00:10:05,627 --> 00:10:06,290
One more chicken.

178
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:07,198
Salted egg, right?

179
00:10:07,198 --> 00:10:08,504
Okay, got it.

180
00:10:08,504 --> 00:10:10,492
Yes, yes.

181
00:10:10,492 --> 00:10:11,492
Alright.

182
00:10:18,282 --> 00:10:19,027
Wait, Chai.

183
00:10:19,027 --> 00:10:20,260
What?

184
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:23,924
I feel dizzy...something feels weird.

185
00:10:23,924 --> 00:10:25,993
Well, you were dancing like crazy just now.

186
00:10:25,993 --> 00:10:29,588
Go, take a rest.
I’ll handle the salad.

187
00:10:29,588 --> 00:10:30,588
Huh?

188
00:10:30,897 --> 00:10:32,897
Are we really selling this too, Chai?

189
00:10:35,769 --> 00:10:39,278
Larb Leuat, spicy pork with raw blood. Looks delicious.

190
00:10:39,278 --> 00:10:41,278
Damn, that’s so red.

191
00:10:42,828 --> 00:10:43,828
That’s pork larb.

192
00:10:46,968 --> 00:10:49,968
You’re not looking good, Sky.
Go rest, I’ll take care of it.

193
00:10:58,195 --> 00:10:59,195
It’s ready, it’s ready.

194
00:11:01,471 --> 00:11:03,221
Here you go. Please enjoy.

195
00:11:03,221 --> 00:11:04,890
Would you like to order?

196
00:11:04,890 --> 00:11:06,318
We can make anything you want.

197
00:11:06,318 --> 00:11:07,466
What would you like?

198
00:11:07,466 --> 00:11:08,381
I’ll take Salted egg papaya salad.

199
00:11:08,381 --> 00:11:09,381
Got it.

200
00:11:26,331 --> 00:11:28,802
Wait...didn’t that girl just hold my hand a moment ago?

201
00:11:28,802 --> 00:11:29,802
Maybe I was seeing things.

202
00:11:30,675 --> 00:11:33,675
Please hold on, I’ll make it the very best for you.

203
00:11:49,023 --> 00:11:50,023
Let me sit down first.

204
00:11:56,652 --> 00:11:59,198
Damn, do you think we’ve been working too hard?

205
00:11:59,198 --> 00:12:03,198
Yeah, right. Hey, how about you,
is your stomachache gone?

206
00:12:03,665 --> 00:12:06,932
No, I still can’t shit.
Took medicine but it’s not helping.

207
00:12:06,932 --> 00:12:10,484
Shit, same here.
I’ve got a splitting headache.

208
00:12:10,484 --> 00:12:12,484
Feels like my migraine’s about to explode.
Pills don’t help.

209
00:12:14,997 --> 00:12:17,506
You dumbass, serves you right.

210
00:12:17,506 --> 00:12:19,493
Huh, Tid-Gift?

211
00:12:19,493 --> 00:12:19,880
Huh?

212
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,389
Did you just call me names?

213
00:12:21,389 --> 00:12:24,577
Why the hell would I?
I barely have the energy to talk.

214
00:12:24,577 --> 00:12:26,568
Then whose voice was that?

215
00:12:26,568 --> 00:12:27,995
It sounded just like you.

216
00:12:27,995 --> 00:12:29,995
I don’t know.
I didn’t say anything.

217
00:12:32,065 --> 00:12:35,065
Ugh, my stomach hurts.
It’s torture.

218
00:12:36,810 --> 00:12:40,398
If you wanna cure that stomachache, try eating my foot.

219
00:12:40,398 --> 00:12:41,504
Eat your own damn foot.

220
00:12:41,504 --> 00:12:42,339
Why don't you do that shit alone?

221
00:12:42,339 --> 00:12:44,124
Huh? What the hell’s wrong with you?

222
00:12:44,124 --> 00:12:45,395
What did you just say?

223
00:12:45,395 --> 00:12:46,589
I didn’t say anything.

224
00:12:46,589 --> 00:12:47,704
You just did.

225
00:12:47,704 --> 00:12:49,704
I’m sitting here massaging my head.
When would I even talk?

226
00:12:52,288 --> 00:12:53,288
Whose voice was that then?

227
00:12:55,078 --> 00:12:56,078
Shut the hell up, bitch.

228
00:12:56,263 --> 00:12:57,607
You shut the hell up.

229
00:12:57,607 --> 00:12:58,643
No, you shut the hell up.

230
00:12:58,643 --> 00:13:01,078
I don’t have time to fight with you, Tid-Gift.
I said I’ve got a headache.

231
00:13:01,078 --> 00:13:03,185
And I’ve got a stomachache.
I don’t wanna fight either.

232
00:13:03,185 --> 00:13:04,171
So why the hell are you yelling at me?

233
00:13:04,171 --> 00:13:05,400
I didn’t yell.

234
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,387
I’m not in the mood to fight.

235
00:13:06,387 --> 00:13:07,414
Go sit over there.

236
00:13:07,414 --> 00:13:08,414
Damn stomachache, bitch.

237
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:14,867
Stupid cow. If you can’t take it, go run into a plane.

238
00:13:14,867 --> 00:13:18,867
Lying about your stomach just to get attention.

239
00:13:18,975 --> 00:13:21,402
Hey, are you trying to piss me off?

240
00:13:21,402 --> 00:13:22,868
You’re the one pissing me off.

241
00:13:22,868 --> 00:13:25,023
I moved over here and you’re still shouting at me.

242
00:13:25,023 --> 00:13:26,409
Can you stop picking a fight with me?

243
00:13:26,409 --> 00:13:27,205
You stop.

244
00:13:27,205 --> 00:13:28,039
Wanna fight it out then?

245
00:13:28,039 --> 00:13:28,710
Yeah, fight it out.

246
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:29,710
Yeah.

247
00:13:32,378 --> 00:13:34,378
I’ve got a headache, damn it.

248
00:13:57,047 --> 00:14:01,047
Madam, Shaman Manfah has been performing the ritual all night.

249
00:14:01,362 --> 00:14:02,753
She’s still sitting here.

250
00:14:02,753 --> 00:14:06,098
Yeah, it’s been so long. Must be a big ritual.

251
00:14:06,098 --> 00:14:10,099
But sitting still like that...she’s still breathing, right?

252
00:14:12,895 --> 00:14:13,963
What are you doing?

253
00:14:13,963 --> 00:14:20,077
Uh, well, seeing you meditate like this all night, I thought maybe…

254
00:14:20,077 --> 00:14:21,630
It’s fine.

255
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,630
I was just asleep.

256
00:14:24,303 --> 00:14:26,253
Sleeping without closing her eyes....

257
00:14:26,253 --> 00:14:30,123
oh, such powerful magic. Praise you, Madame.

258
00:14:30,123 --> 00:14:33,438
And what about casting spells on those people?

259
00:14:33,438 --> 00:14:37,229
I finished that last night.

260
00:14:37,229 --> 00:14:38,577
And what’s the result?

261
00:14:38,577 --> 00:14:41,690
They’re already in chaos.

262
00:14:41,690 --> 00:14:43,690
Bring me the board.

263
00:14:46,285 --> 00:14:52,195
These two, my child spirits gave them neck and back pain.

264
00:14:52,195 --> 00:14:56,195
Those two women, I buried black magic in their head and stomach.

265
00:14:56,227 --> 00:14:59,293
Now they’re hearing voices, hallucinating.

266
00:14:59,293 --> 00:15:03,191
That man, he was attacked by widow spirits,

267
00:15:03,191 --> 00:15:04,191
drained of all strength.

268
00:15:05,854 --> 00:15:08,488
And that one, her face already looks like a ghost.

269
00:15:08,488 --> 00:15:11,243
But I sent a ogre spirit into her body,

270
00:15:11,243 --> 00:15:13,714
so she craves only rotten food.

271
00:15:13,714 --> 00:15:16,714
Soon enough the spirit will eat her alive.

272
00:15:18,742 --> 00:15:20,692
That’s so cruel.

273
00:15:20,692 --> 00:15:22,368
But it’s still not satisfying.

274
00:15:22,368 --> 00:15:24,114
I want them to suffer even more.

275
00:15:24,114 --> 00:15:25,668
Then pay me extra.

276
00:15:25,668 --> 00:15:26,905
No problem.

277
00:15:26,905 --> 00:15:29,255
If you can make them worse...

278
00:15:29,255 --> 00:15:32,411
I’ve got no problem with that either.

279
00:15:32,411 --> 00:15:36,412
At last, we’ll see their downfall.

280
00:15:37,207 --> 00:15:40,207
Yes, Madam. They won’t survive.

281
00:15:43,641 --> 00:15:44,312
Quiet.

282
00:15:44,312 --> 00:15:45,312
Oh dear!

283
00:15:45,496 --> 00:15:47,972
I need to focus my concentration to increase my power.

284
00:15:47,972 --> 00:15:48,972
Oh, sorry!

285
00:15:49,797 --> 00:15:50,797
Please, please.

286
00:15:58,066 --> 00:15:59,066
Hey!

287
00:15:59,861 --> 00:16:00,861
Sorry, sorry!

288
00:16:12,196 --> 00:16:13,196
I'm having such a great time with you, Ploy.

289
00:16:17,827 --> 00:16:19,827
I'm having such a great time with you too, Chai.

290
00:16:24,018 --> 00:16:25,683
That's what I thought.

291
00:16:25,683 --> 00:16:28,232
You're here...

292
00:16:28,232 --> 00:16:30,232
What? Ploy and I just...

293
00:16:33,129 --> 00:16:34,129
Where did she go?

294
00:16:34,198 --> 00:16:36,790
You’re getting more psycho each day.

295
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:39,459
Are you crazy? Ploy just wanted...

296
00:16:39,459 --> 00:16:42,575
some kind of special excitement.

297
00:16:42,575 --> 00:16:44,575
Ploy? Which Ploy?

298
00:16:46,523 --> 00:16:47,670
She was probably just shy of you.

299
00:16:47,670 --> 00:16:50,781
See? The condom’s still right here.

300
00:16:50,781 --> 00:16:52,691
But the sex was so good.

301
00:16:52,691 --> 00:16:55,638
Finish once, go again. Finish again, go again.

302
00:16:55,638 --> 00:16:57,866
I told her to stop, she wouldn’t.

303
00:16:57,866 --> 00:16:59,415
Guess she really was that good.

304
00:16:59,415 --> 00:17:01,521
You’re looking pale and yellow.

305
00:17:01,521 --> 00:17:02,959
What do you mean, pale and yellow?

306
00:17:02,959 --> 00:17:06,959
If she were still here, I’d take her back for another two or three rounds.

307
00:17:08,153 --> 00:17:09,904
Come on, let’s go eat.

308
00:17:09,904 --> 00:17:10,904
Let me wash my hands first.

309
00:17:20,690 --> 00:17:21,690
Everything looks so delicious.

310
00:17:22,999 --> 00:17:24,999
Why is it all raw food though?

311
00:17:25,394 --> 00:17:26,394
Raw food?

312
00:17:26,981 --> 00:17:27,981
It looks amazing.

313
00:17:29,215 --> 00:17:30,215
Are you an ogre or what?

314
00:17:30,963 --> 00:17:31,963
What ogre?

315
00:17:32,429 --> 00:17:33,654
Looking this gorgeous?

316
00:17:33,654 --> 00:17:35,654
And all popular...

317
00:17:37,121 --> 00:17:38,112
Oh, looks delicious.

318
00:17:38,112 --> 00:17:40,112
Oh, raw pork. Want some?

319
00:17:41,908 --> 00:17:42,908
No, thanks.

320
00:17:44,701 --> 00:17:46,701
Ploy is following me for another round.

321
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:50,250
Shall we go, Ploy?

322
00:17:59,405 --> 00:18:00,405
Ploy.

323
00:18:01,032 --> 00:18:02,032
Ploy, who?

324
00:18:03,777 --> 00:18:04,777
Crazy.

325
00:18:15,365 --> 00:18:16,365
Ploy...

326
00:18:17,193 --> 00:18:18,193
Ploy...

327
00:18:19,901 --> 00:18:20,901
Ploy...

328
00:18:21,293 --> 00:18:22,293
Ploy...

329
00:18:24,727 --> 00:18:25,727
Chai...

330
00:18:28,163 --> 00:18:29,163
Chai...

331
00:18:36,231 --> 00:18:38,231
Ploy...Ploy...

332
00:18:39,146 --> 00:18:40,146
Ploy...

333
00:18:41,013 --> 00:18:42,013
Ploy...

334
00:18:42,164 --> 00:18:50,599
Ploy, I'm here.

335
00:18:50,599 --> 00:18:53,189
Ploy, I'm here, don't go.

336
00:18:53,189 --> 00:18:55,856
Ploy, I'm here.

337
00:18:55,856 --> 00:18:56,856
Ploy.

338
00:19:00,007 --> 00:19:02,714
Oh, Ploy.

339
00:19:02,714 --> 00:19:06,714
You want to continue, Chai? Or...

340
00:19:07,746 --> 00:19:09,737
you seem exhausted...

341
00:19:09,737 --> 00:19:11,642
Don't put it that way.

342
00:19:11,642 --> 00:19:15,643
I'm all on it, I'm unstoppable.

343
00:19:24,476 --> 00:19:28,476
Wait, Ploy, do you wanna do it in the cockpit?

344
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:30,780
Or on the plane's wing?

345
00:19:32,050 --> 00:19:34,000
Let me give you a few more rounds.

346
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:37,000
More? Okay, let's go.

347
00:19:45,278 --> 00:19:47,466
Damn, this really hurts.
It's worse than last time.

348
00:19:47,466 --> 00:19:49,739
Maybe you and I need to see a doctor for a full checkup.

349
00:19:49,739 --> 00:19:52,888
Yeah, good idea.
It hurts like hell right now.

350
00:19:52,888 --> 00:19:56,037
Feels like I twisted my neck.
Look, I can only turn this far.

351
00:19:56,037 --> 00:19:58,187
Yeah, don’t turn.
Just go back the other way.

352
00:19:58,187 --> 00:19:59,656
From now on, don’t fly with me anymore.

353
00:19:59,656 --> 00:20:02,648
Yeah, of course.
I won’t fly with you either.

354
00:20:02,648 --> 00:20:03,648
I’ve had enough of you.

355
00:20:06,637 --> 00:20:07,637
My head hurts.

356
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:11,430
Shit, who laughed?

357
00:20:11,498 --> 00:20:12,498
Are you hallucinating?

358
00:20:13,134 --> 00:20:15,003
I didn’t hear any laughter at all.

359
00:20:17,549 --> 00:20:19,549
Well, I did hear crying just now.

360
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:20,940
What's that?

361
00:20:22,088 --> 00:20:23,396
What’s wrong with you two?

362
00:20:23,396 --> 00:20:24,396
I don’t hear anything.

363
00:20:25,906 --> 00:20:27,217
Maybe they’re just hungry.

364
00:20:27,217 --> 00:20:28,569
Here, I bought some snacks.

365
00:20:28,569 --> 00:20:29,564
Want some?

366
00:20:29,564 --> 00:20:31,199
Yeah, I’m hungry too.

367
00:20:31,199 --> 00:20:31,906
This custard looks good.

368
00:20:31,906 --> 00:20:32,536
Tid-Gift, come here.

369
00:20:32,536 --> 00:20:33,536
Give me one.

370
00:20:40,005 --> 00:20:42,681
Auntie, this is so good.
Want to try?

371
00:20:42,681 --> 00:20:43,681
No thanks, dear.

372
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:50,977
Mmm, this is really delicious.

373
00:20:50,977 --> 00:20:51,977
You really don’t want any, Auntie?

374
00:20:53,650 --> 00:20:54,650
Uh…

375
00:20:54,875 --> 00:20:57,709
Everyone looks a bit strange.

376
00:20:57,709 --> 00:20:59,742
Like you’re under a spell.

377
00:20:59,742 --> 00:21:00,732
Huh?

378
00:21:00,732 --> 00:21:04,642
Like being cursed? Like with black magic or something, Auntie?

379
00:21:04,642 --> 00:21:07,948
Yes. I think you should consult a shaman first.

380
00:21:07,948 --> 00:21:09,948
There’s no such nonsense.

381
00:21:10,495 --> 00:21:12,347
All-New and I were thinking of seeing a doctor.

382
00:21:12,347 --> 00:21:14,006
But at a hospital.

383
00:21:14,006 --> 00:21:14,549
What for?

384
00:21:14,549 --> 00:21:15,609
I’ve got neck pain.

385
00:21:15,609 --> 00:21:16,783
He’s got back pain.

386
00:21:16,783 --> 00:21:19,617
Medicine doesn’t help, so we thought of a thorough checkup.

387
00:21:19,617 --> 00:21:20,085
Yeah.

388
00:21:20,085 --> 00:21:22,085
The clinic behind the office is useless.

389
00:21:25,872 --> 00:21:26,872
See you.

390
00:21:29,899 --> 00:21:30,899
Why so dramatic?

391
00:21:31,695 --> 00:21:34,140
Auntie, what do you mean we’ve been cursed?

392
00:21:34,140 --> 00:21:36,640
A friend of mine who got cursed looked exactly like this.

393
00:21:38,089 --> 00:21:40,958
Don’t tell me...you feel cursed too?

394
00:21:40,958 --> 00:21:43,914
Of course I do.
We’ve been hearing strange voices for a while, right?

395
00:21:43,914 --> 00:21:45,263
Yeah, true.

396
00:21:45,263 --> 00:21:49,263
Auntie, do you know any shaman who can lift a curse?

397
00:21:49,684 --> 00:21:51,997
Yes, I know a very skilled one.

398
00:21:51,997 --> 00:21:53,394
His name is Shaman Akkee.

399
00:21:53,394 --> 00:21:55,827
Wait, did you say Atkee?

400
00:21:55,827 --> 00:21:56,856
Akkee.

401
00:21:56,856 --> 00:21:58,322
Oh, Akkee. Okay.

402
00:21:58,322 --> 00:21:59,555
Yes, Akkee.

403
00:21:59,555 --> 00:22:02,555
Shaman Akkee.
Just the name sounds ancient.

404
00:22:08,741 --> 00:22:11,008
Hey Sky, why didn’t you bring Chai with you?

405
00:22:11,008 --> 00:22:13,270
In case the whole office is cursed, he could get treated too.

406
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:15,944
He’s too busy with sex.
I asked but he wouldn’t come.

407
00:22:15,944 --> 00:22:18,944
Hey, aren’t you worried about him?
Why don’t you help Chai?

408
00:22:20,296 --> 00:22:23,282
I don’t care. Right now, I just want to save myself.

409
00:22:23,282 --> 00:22:24,282
Forget the rest.

410
00:22:24,517 --> 00:22:25,517
Fine, bring him later then.

411
00:22:25,915 --> 00:22:28,915
So what now?
The shaman is meditating.

412
00:22:30,509 --> 00:22:33,464
By the way, he’s kinda hot, huh?

413
00:22:33,464 --> 00:22:34,464
Look at his muscles.

414
00:22:35,138 --> 00:22:36,138
I’ll take care of this.

415
00:22:36,484 --> 00:22:37,484
What are you doing, Sky?

416
00:22:38,751 --> 00:22:41,751
I’ll pretend to kiss him, show him I love him.

417
00:22:45,418 --> 00:22:47,418
You were hit by an explosion, right?

418
00:22:48,773 --> 00:22:49,773
That’s the one.

419
00:22:49,963 --> 00:22:51,963
Uh, I liked popping pimples when I was a kid.

420
00:22:52,986 --> 00:22:54,986
I mean, you’ve been cursed, right?

421
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:58,691
A black curse too.
We must get it out quickly.

422
00:22:58,691 --> 00:22:59,724
You knew?

423
00:23:00,393 --> 00:23:03,020
Then can you remove it for us?

424
00:23:03,020 --> 00:23:05,651
And if you remove the curse,

425
00:23:05,651 --> 00:23:07,651
can we replace it with yours instead?

426
00:23:08,407 --> 00:23:10,407
Sky, he’s a white shaman.

427
00:23:11,518 --> 00:23:14,952
Um, but Shaman, is yours really white?

428
00:23:14,952 --> 00:23:15,952
Yes, it’s white.

429
00:23:17,222 --> 00:23:19,372
If it’s white, is it big?

430
00:23:19,372 --> 00:23:22,086
Mhm, of course it’s big.

431
00:23:22,086 --> 00:23:25,678
Wow. Is it long too?

432
00:23:25,678 --> 00:23:27,585
Around fifty-nine.

433
00:23:27,585 --> 00:23:30,976
Shit, fifty-nine?

434
00:23:30,976 --> 00:23:32,976
I mean the offering for the sacred string.

435
00:23:34,482 --> 00:23:38,030
White thread, big roll, long strand.
Fifty-nine baht. What are you thinking?

436
00:23:38,030 --> 00:23:41,102
We weren’t thinking anything.
Nothing dirty at all.

437
00:23:41,102 --> 00:23:43,713
Then let’s remove it.

438
00:23:43,713 --> 00:23:46,659
Of course.
Let’s start with this one.

439
00:23:46,659 --> 00:23:51,159
Uh, my name is Chaba.
Am I first?

440
00:23:56,848 --> 00:23:57,848
Put your hands together.

441
00:23:58,999 --> 00:23:59,999
Namo.

442
00:24:00,665 --> 00:24:01,665
Mumaai

443
00:24:02,531 --> 00:24:03,531
Thayamano,

444
00:24:04,354 --> 00:24:05,354
Thayamano,

445
00:24:06,273 --> 00:24:07,273
Thayamano,

446
00:24:09,062 --> 00:24:10,057
Is that a spell?

447
00:24:10,057 --> 00:24:11,057
Move closer.

448
00:24:20,307 --> 00:24:21,015
Is it out?

449
00:24:21,015 --> 00:24:24,366
The knife is cold.
I felt a chill just now.

450
00:24:24,366 --> 00:24:25,366
Shit.

451
00:24:33,479 --> 00:24:36,479
Your curse is gone.
Next, your turn.

452
00:24:37,994 --> 00:24:39,465
My name is Sky.

453
00:24:39,465 --> 00:24:40,465
Yours is the worst of all.

454
00:24:41,771 --> 00:24:45,771
Looks like my knife alone won’t work.

455
00:24:48,081 --> 00:24:49,081
For this, I need this one.

456
00:24:50,231 --> 00:24:51,231
That’s huge!

457
00:24:52,500 --> 00:24:54,976
Are you going to cut fish with that, Shaman?

458
00:24:54,976 --> 00:24:56,976
Sit in the middle and put your hands together.

459
00:25:13,956 --> 00:25:15,956
Are you removing the curse, or my whole family line?

460
00:25:19,445 --> 00:25:21,445
There’s a spirit inside this one.

461
00:25:22,594 --> 00:25:23,594
It must be removed.

462
00:25:27,422 --> 00:25:29,422
Hey, is it out, Sky?

463
00:25:29,693 --> 00:25:31,693
Cramp, damn, cramp!

464
00:25:33,247 --> 00:25:34,247
Ready?

465
00:25:45,675 --> 00:25:46,675
Are you cured?

466
00:25:46,708 --> 00:25:47,708
Tid-Gift.

467
00:25:47,783 --> 00:25:48,783
It’s gone. You’re cured.

468
00:25:50,407 --> 00:25:52,407
Shaman, Shaman, thank you so much.

469
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:06,501
Madam, she isn’t asleep again, right?

470
00:26:06,501 --> 00:26:07,501
Check her, check her.

471
00:26:14,776 --> 00:26:16,645
Madame, what happened?

472
00:26:16,645 --> 00:26:19,271
They found out we cursed them.

473
00:26:19,271 --> 00:26:21,064
What, how did they know?

474
00:26:21,064 --> 00:26:23,773
I don’t know, but they’re about to remove it.

475
00:26:23,773 --> 00:26:27,522
No, Madame, we must ruin their lives no matter what.

476
00:26:27,522 --> 00:26:29,236
Who’s removing their curse?

477
00:26:29,236 --> 00:26:30,862
It’s Akkee.

478
00:26:30,862 --> 00:26:31,733
Akkee?

479
00:26:31,733 --> 00:26:32,082
Yes.

480
00:26:32,082 --> 00:26:32,875
I knew it.

481
00:26:32,875 --> 00:26:34,269
Madam, do you know him?

482
00:26:34,269 --> 00:26:35,269
No.

483
00:26:36,624 --> 00:26:39,172
But he must be someone with strong magic.
Akkee, like “fire.”

484
00:26:39,172 --> 00:26:40,172
Something like that.

485
00:26:41,965 --> 00:26:43,675
You don’t know anything.

486
00:26:43,675 --> 00:26:46,907
Akkee is a white shaman.

487
00:26:46,907 --> 00:26:49,374
He’s been my rival for a long time.

488
00:26:49,374 --> 00:26:53,203
But in elementary school,
the PE teacher told me that the black belt was the best.

489
00:26:53,203 --> 00:26:54,203
Hey, that’s Taekwondo.

490
00:26:55,831 --> 00:26:57,504
What now, Madame?

491
00:26:57,504 --> 00:27:00,777
I must meditate first...because right now,

492
00:27:00,777 --> 00:27:02,777
I’ve lost a lot of energy.

493
00:27:11,724 --> 00:27:13,311
It’s your turn, Tid-Gift.

494
00:27:13,311 --> 00:27:15,311
I’m telling you, it’s torture.

495
00:27:16,254 --> 00:27:17,254
You.

496
00:27:18,201 --> 00:27:19,830
My name is Tid-Gift, Shaman.

497
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:22,416
Your curse was placed in your stomach.

498
00:27:22,416 --> 00:27:24,043
That's serious, Miss.

499
00:27:24,043 --> 00:27:26,184
Wow, he talks so politely with Tid-Gift.

500
00:27:26,184 --> 00:27:28,256
But with you, he said you got blown up.

501
00:27:28,256 --> 00:27:32,001
You two, go wait outside the curtain.

502
00:27:32,001 --> 00:27:34,001
Because Tid-Gift’s curse is so strong,

503
00:27:34,074 --> 00:27:36,074
I’m afraid what comes out might get into you two.

504
00:27:37,428 --> 00:27:38,857
No, no.

505
00:27:38,857 --> 00:27:40,732
Please help my friend, Shaman.

506
00:27:40,732 --> 00:27:41,405
Yes.

507
00:27:41,405 --> 00:27:42,405
Go quickly, I’m scared.

508
00:27:42,632 --> 00:27:43,632
No, it might enter me.

509
00:27:43,904 --> 00:27:44,904
Wait.

510
00:27:45,650 --> 00:27:46,650
Close the curtain.

511
00:27:46,961 --> 00:27:47,155
Close the curtain?

512
00:27:47,155 --> 00:27:48,142
Close it tight.

513
00:27:48,142 --> 00:27:49,142
Please close the curtain, Tid-Gift.

514
00:27:51,258 --> 00:27:52,258
It's my turn now.

515
00:27:52,763 --> 00:27:53,630
Stay strong.

516
00:27:53,630 --> 00:27:54,630
Stay strong, Tid-Gift.

517
00:27:56,786 --> 00:27:57,786
Tid-Gift.

518
00:27:58,057 --> 00:27:59,057
Take off your clothes.

519
00:28:00,045 --> 00:28:01,045
Take off the clothes?

520
00:28:01,547 --> 00:28:02,547
I’m ready, Shaman.

521
00:28:02,932 --> 00:28:04,932
It’ll be painful. I’m starting now.

522
00:28:05,642 --> 00:28:06,642
The ritual begins.

523
00:28:07,470 --> 00:28:08,698
Oh wow.

524
00:28:08,698 --> 00:28:10,648
Woo, Shaman.

525
00:28:10,648 --> 00:28:11,882
Ohhh.

526
00:28:11,882 --> 00:28:12,882
Doesn’t it sound strange to you?

527
00:28:12,910 --> 00:28:16,910
The painful screams sound almost fun.

528
00:28:16,938 --> 00:28:17,646
Ohhh.

529
00:28:17,646 --> 00:28:18,592
You okay?

530
00:28:18,592 --> 00:28:20,468
Amazing, Shaman.

531
00:28:20,468 --> 00:28:22,016
Ooooh.

532
00:28:22,016 --> 00:28:24,205
Her voice...Tid-Gift almost sounds like she’s enjoying it.

533
00:28:24,917 --> 00:28:27,066
If I could, I’d take her pain instead.

534
00:28:27,066 --> 00:28:28,019
I’ll go in and help her.

535
00:28:28,019 --> 00:28:31,135
Don’t. He’s doing the ritual,
the curse might get into you.

536
00:28:31,135 --> 00:28:33,410
Swear to God you really mean that.

537
00:28:33,410 --> 00:28:34,476
Tid-Gift.

538
00:28:34,476 --> 00:28:35,628
Fifty-nine.

539
00:28:36,771 --> 00:28:37,562
Is it white?

540
00:28:37,562 --> 00:28:39,187
So white.

541
00:28:39,187 --> 00:28:39,934
Is it big?

542
00:28:39,934 --> 00:28:40,931
So big.

543
00:28:42,798 --> 00:28:44,798
Mhm, it’s almost done.

544
00:28:48,951 --> 00:28:49,951
How are you?

545
00:28:50,779 --> 00:28:51,779
It’s gone.

546
00:28:52,613 --> 00:28:53,613
That curse must’ve been strong.

547
00:28:54,525 --> 00:28:57,514
Look at the Shaman, he’s dripping with sweat.

548
00:28:57,514 --> 00:29:00,664
Even his buttons popped open, the curse burst them apart.

549
00:29:00,664 --> 00:29:02,664
Oh my, you’re right.

550
00:29:04,053 --> 00:29:05,053
Yes.

551
00:29:05,601 --> 00:29:09,601
Tid-Gift’s curse was no ordinary curse.

552
00:29:10,635 --> 00:29:14,635
And your power is no ordinary power either.

553
00:29:15,671 --> 00:29:17,177
What the hell, Tid-Gift?

554
00:29:17,177 --> 00:29:22,685
I mean his spell and incantations.
They’re extraordinary too.

555
00:29:22,685 --> 00:29:23,685
Top-notch work.

556
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:25,960
You think so, right?

557
00:29:26,869 --> 00:29:27,869
I think so.

558
00:29:29,615 --> 00:29:30,615
Did Tid-Gift take it all?

559
00:29:46,970 --> 00:29:48,153
Madame, Madame!

560
00:29:48,153 --> 00:29:50,103
Madame, what’s happening?

561
00:29:51,133 --> 00:29:52,133
Madame!

562
00:29:52,449 --> 00:29:53,722
They removed the curse.

563
00:29:53,722 --> 00:29:54,677
Oh, no!

564
00:29:54,677 --> 00:29:55,586
Three of them.

565
00:29:56,061 --> 00:29:59,369
No, Madame, you must cast a new curse.

566
00:29:59,369 --> 00:30:00,675
Make it even heavier.

567
00:30:00,675 --> 00:30:01,790
Are you serious, Madam?

568
00:30:04,241 --> 00:30:05,241
Madam, what are you doing?

569
00:30:09,308 --> 00:30:11,615
Hey, are you casting spells on us?

570
00:30:11,615 --> 00:30:13,485
Yes. What are you gonna do about it?

571
00:30:13,485 --> 00:30:14,485
So this stuff is real?

572
00:30:15,393 --> 00:30:17,468
I’ve got neck pain, he’s got back pain.

573
00:30:17,468 --> 00:30:20,535
That’s because you’re useless.
I had no choice.

574
00:30:20,535 --> 00:30:22,802
If it’s like this, I’ll tell everyone.

575
00:30:22,802 --> 00:30:24,272
So you’re making yourself my enemy?

576
00:30:24,272 --> 00:30:26,272
Madam, this is too much.

577
00:30:28,026 --> 00:30:32,027
So these two are useless to us now, right?

578
00:30:33,098 --> 00:30:35,289
Seems like it.

579
00:30:35,289 --> 00:30:37,154
Siri, move over there.

580
00:30:37,154 --> 00:30:37,382
Yes.

581
00:30:37,382 --> 00:30:40,382
I’ll make this fabulous, just watch.

582
00:30:49,290 --> 00:30:50,290
Do it!

583
00:30:51,925 --> 00:30:52,925
Louder.

584
00:30:54,401 --> 00:30:55,401
Louder, louder.

585
00:31:06,623 --> 00:31:08,891
Hey, All-New, Kreetha.

586
00:31:08,891 --> 00:31:12,237
Why get so excited?
They just fainted.

587
00:31:12,237 --> 00:31:15,145
So what do we do next?
Our plan’s ruined.

588
00:31:15,145 --> 00:31:16,620
It doesn’t matter.

589
00:31:16,620 --> 00:31:20,331
Because I’ll use those two for the next plan.

590
00:31:20,331 --> 00:31:21,320
What plan?

591
00:31:21,320 --> 00:31:25,320
I’ll hypnotize them to attack the others.

592
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:29,296
Wow, really?

593
00:31:29,296 --> 00:31:30,886
But Madam Porn won’t approve.

594
00:31:30,886 --> 00:31:31,480
Even better.

595
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,390
What?

596
00:31:32,390 --> 00:31:33,390
Let’s do what she says.

597
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:35,660
We’ve come this far already.

598
00:31:36,526 --> 00:31:37,526
We must destroy them completely.

599
00:31:51,942 --> 00:31:55,891
Don’t worry, I will cover this meal.

600
00:31:55,891 --> 00:31:56,886
No, it’s fine.

601
00:31:56,886 --> 00:32:00,886
No way, you went through all the trouble to remove our curse.

602
00:32:02,232 --> 00:32:06,232
I wish I could get cursed again.
That ritual knife was amazing.

603
00:32:07,302 --> 00:32:10,727
Are you sure you’re hooked on the Shaman’s knife?

604
00:32:10,727 --> 00:32:12,727
I’m hooked.
His knife is really good.

605
00:32:16,123 --> 00:32:18,356
Sounds like it wasn’t just the knife,

606
00:32:18,356 --> 00:32:20,348
more like she's enjoying it too much.

607
00:32:20,348 --> 00:32:24,348
By the way, Shaman, do you know who cursed us?

608
00:32:24,521 --> 00:32:27,115
Mhm, I’ve got an idea.

609
00:32:27,115 --> 00:32:27,788
Who?

610
00:32:27,788 --> 00:32:29,777
This kind of black magic…

611
00:32:29,777 --> 00:32:30,777
Must be Madame Manfah.

612
00:32:32,569 --> 00:32:34,957
I only know “Han Fah.”

613
00:32:34,957 --> 00:32:36,148
But who is she?

614
00:32:36,148 --> 00:32:40,148
A sorceress, skilled in dark arts.

615
00:32:41,104 --> 00:32:44,457
And who would hire a shaman to curse us?

616
00:32:44,457 --> 00:32:45,457
Good question.

617
00:32:49,207 --> 00:32:52,392
Hey, All-New, Kreetha, sit down.

618
00:32:52,392 --> 00:32:54,739
What are you doing?
Let us join you.

619
00:32:54,739 --> 00:32:57,132
Yeah, All-New, Kreetha, sit.

620
00:32:57,132 --> 00:33:00,279
This is Shaman Akkee, the one who lifted our curse.

621
00:33:00,279 --> 00:33:03,386
Pleasure to meet you.

622
00:33:03,386 --> 00:33:06,288
You two didn’t get cursed too?

623
00:33:06,288 --> 00:33:09,156
The way you talk, your faces look strange.

624
00:33:09,156 --> 00:33:12,463
Nonsense, that stuff isn’t real.

625
00:33:12,463 --> 00:33:15,494
These two aren’t afraid of curses.
They’re Gen Alpha kids.

626
00:33:15,494 --> 00:33:19,494
All they know is Tung Tung Tung Tung Tung Sahula.

627
00:33:19,959 --> 00:33:20,865
What does that even mean?

628
00:33:20,865 --> 00:33:24,092
You wouldn’t know.
You’re a baby boomer.

629
00:33:24,092 --> 00:33:26,092
Old people don’t know these things.

630
00:33:26,283 --> 00:33:29,283
We weren’t cursed, but we have something for you.

631
00:33:35,184 --> 00:33:37,184
These two were hypnotized with black magic.

632
00:33:40,488 --> 00:33:42,488
Taya Na Mo Phutthaya Sangkhara.

633
00:33:49,563 --> 00:33:50,563
Na Mo Phutthaya.

634
00:33:54,278 --> 00:33:56,073
Tie the sacred string around them.

635
00:33:56,073 --> 00:33:57,073
Quick, help me.

636
00:33:59,184 --> 00:34:00,184
Pull tighter, pull tighter.

637
00:34:00,217 --> 00:34:01,217
Tie it around their heads too.

638
00:34:03,131 --> 00:34:04,038
You’re too slow.

639
00:34:04,038 --> 00:34:05,038
Okay, okay!

640
00:34:15,667 --> 00:34:16,732
How the hell did I end up here?

641
00:34:16,732 --> 00:34:19,199
You two got possessed and attacked us.

642
00:34:19,199 --> 00:34:20,670
Possessed? There’s no such thing.

643
00:34:20,670 --> 00:34:22,670
No? Then look at this.

644
00:34:31,466 --> 00:34:32,466
Well, I’ll be damned.

645
00:34:32,814 --> 00:34:34,814
Good thing the Shaman came to save us.

646
00:34:42,605 --> 00:34:46,605
When will you stop meddling in my business, Akkee?

647
00:34:47,961 --> 00:34:48,961
Madame Manfah.

648
00:34:50,351 --> 00:34:54,147
So this is Madame Manfah,

649
00:34:54,147 --> 00:34:56,259
the one who cursed us.

650
00:34:56,259 --> 00:34:58,133
Of course.

651
00:34:58,133 --> 00:35:00,133
But that damn Shaman interfered with me.

652
00:35:00,799 --> 00:35:04,799
Today you won’t escape, Akkee.

653
00:35:05,232 --> 00:35:06,232
See this?

654
00:35:08,488 --> 00:35:09,720
Don’t tell me…

655
00:35:09,720 --> 00:35:12,755
you’re going to put my spirit into that doll.

656
00:35:12,755 --> 00:35:13,755
Of course.

657
00:35:28,504 --> 00:35:30,496
If you see him like this,

658
00:35:30,496 --> 00:35:32,496
would you still respect him?

659
00:35:34,328 --> 00:35:35,328
Then stand up.

660
00:35:40,078 --> 00:35:41,078
Get up.

661
00:35:41,548 --> 00:35:45,548
Try this pose. The legendary move.

662
00:35:45,583 --> 00:35:48,376
Alright, start, grab your crotch.

663
00:35:48,376 --> 00:35:49,376
Hand up.

664
00:35:50,525 --> 00:35:55,101
Go, go, go!

665
00:35:55,101 --> 00:35:56,101
Looks fun, huh?

666
00:35:56,374 --> 00:35:58,969
Go, go!

667
00:35:58,969 --> 00:36:01,441
Another pose then. Side view.

668
00:36:01,441 --> 00:36:02,397
This one,

669
00:36:02,397 --> 00:36:04,584
picking something up.

670
00:36:04,584 --> 00:36:07,852
Down, down, up, up.

671
00:36:07,852 --> 00:36:09,721
Down, down, down.

672
00:36:09,721 --> 00:36:13,427
And stick your ass up.

673
00:36:13,427 --> 00:36:15,427
We can’t let this go on.
We have to ruin her power.

674
00:36:16,584 --> 00:36:18,211
What do we do?

675
00:36:18,211 --> 00:36:21,286
I know. Smear her with menstrual blood,
that’ll ruin her curse.

676
00:36:21,286 --> 00:36:23,286
No, that’s disgusting.
Any other way?

677
00:36:25,153 --> 00:36:26,866
Jump over her head.

678
00:36:26,866 --> 00:36:28,375
That’ll definitely ruin it.

679
00:36:28,375 --> 00:36:29,883
Quick, Chaba.
You do it.

680
00:36:29,883 --> 00:36:30,883
The Shaman’s exhausted already.

681
00:36:34,834 --> 00:36:36,944
He actually looks like he’s enjoying it.

682
00:36:36,944 --> 00:36:40,333
No, it can’t be like this.
You jump!

683
00:36:40,333 --> 00:36:43,318
Look at me!
How could I jump over her head?

684
00:36:43,318 --> 00:36:44,390
You do it.

685
00:36:44,390 --> 00:36:47,546
I can’t even get my knees up,
how the hell do I jump?

686
00:36:47,546 --> 00:36:48,302
What do we do then?

687
00:36:48,302 --> 00:36:51,212
I’ll do it. I already passed the test in sixth grade.

688
00:36:51,212 --> 00:36:52,212
Come on.

689
00:36:52,446 --> 00:36:53,446
You’re done for, bitch!

690
00:36:53,792 --> 00:36:55,303
Fight her!

691
00:37:15,496 --> 00:37:16,496
Her power’s gone.

692
00:37:19,169 --> 00:37:20,169
You okay?

693
00:37:23,286 --> 00:37:24,286
She’s out of power.

694
00:37:25,317 --> 00:37:27,317
That’s good. Hey.

695
00:37:28,776 --> 00:37:32,776
Wow, my world.
I am a robot, not a human.

696
00:37:34,283 --> 00:37:38,194
Bluetooth connected.

697
00:37:38,194 --> 00:37:40,194
I am a robot.

698
00:37:41,857 --> 00:37:43,257
I am...bluetooth connected.

699
00:37:44,802 --> 00:37:45,802
Is she a robot shaman?

700
00:37:46,357 --> 00:37:47,357
Yeah.

701
00:37:51,104 --> 00:37:52,104
Now it’s my turn.

702
00:37:57,156 --> 00:37:59,271
Wait, the curse is gone.

703
00:37:59,271 --> 00:37:59,940
It’s ruined.

704
00:37:59,940 --> 00:38:00,455
Oh.

705
00:38:00,455 --> 00:38:02,169
Although, that curse is gone.

706
00:38:02,169 --> 00:38:04,169
But...this one is real.

707
00:38:05,605 --> 00:38:06,552
Tid-Gift.

708
00:38:06,552 --> 00:38:07,298
Yes?

709
00:38:07,298 --> 00:38:08,451
Tid-Gift.

710
00:38:08,451 --> 00:38:09,451
She's trying to hurt me.

711
00:38:10,366 --> 00:38:12,366
Tid-Gift, you slut.

712
00:38:12,523 --> 00:38:13,523
You want to conquer every field, huh?

713
00:38:13,999 --> 00:38:15,788
I've been cursed!

714
00:38:15,788 --> 00:38:17,215
Shaman, I’ve been cursed!

715
00:38:17,215 --> 00:38:18,215
I’m so scared!

716
00:38:26,534 --> 00:38:28,534
Siri, get down here right now.

717
00:38:28,682 --> 00:38:29,682
Why did you do that?

718
00:38:30,192 --> 00:38:31,192
You insulted Madame Manfah badly.

719
00:38:32,700 --> 00:38:36,700
Oh Madam, she’s been gone so long.
She probably didn’t survive.

720
00:38:37,046 --> 00:38:39,842
Besides, the ground is hard.

721
00:38:39,842 --> 00:38:40,842
Get down right now.

722
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:46,543
I think this time it’ll definitely work.

723
00:38:46,543 --> 00:38:49,296
Because Madame Manfah did it herself.

724
00:38:49,296 --> 00:38:50,296
Oh, not necessarily, Madam.

725
00:38:53,533 --> 00:38:56,323
I am a human. I am a robot.

726
00:38:56,323 --> 00:38:58,311
Bluetooth...connected...device...

727
00:38:58,311 --> 00:39:00,377
Bluetooth...to...connect...device...

728
00:39:00,377 --> 00:39:01,377
Madame!

729
00:39:01,489 --> 00:39:02,160
Madam.

730
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:03,160
What’s wrong with Madame Manfah?

731
00:39:07,635 --> 00:39:08,635
She seems strange, Madam.

732
00:39:08,747 --> 00:39:09,572
Yeah.

733
00:39:09,572 --> 00:39:13,572
Could it be that her power has worn off?

734
00:39:13,805 --> 00:39:14,805
What do you mean?

735
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:18,101
I once heard that those who practice black magic...

736
00:39:18,101 --> 00:39:21,693
when their power fades, it backfires on them.

737
00:39:21,693 --> 00:39:25,693
And when it backfires, they lose their minds.

738
00:39:25,806 --> 00:39:27,113
They go completely crazy, Madam.

739
00:39:27,113 --> 00:39:27,906
Oh no!

740
00:39:27,906 --> 00:39:30,015
Bluetooth...to...connect...device...

741
00:39:30,015 --> 00:39:32,015
Siri, do something!

742
00:39:33,747 --> 00:39:38,747
Oh, a robot?
Leave it to me, Madam.

743
00:39:48,736 --> 00:39:51,646
Siri, what are you doing?

744
00:39:51,646 --> 00:39:53,392
Megan, Madam.

745
00:39:53,392 --> 00:39:54,144
Megan?

746
00:39:54,144 --> 00:39:58,144
No robot can beat this one.

747
00:39:59,251 --> 00:40:00,251
Turning off the switch.

748
00:40:01,002 --> 00:40:02,002
It’s here, alright?

749
00:40:03,153 --> 00:40:04,153
Turning off the switch.

750
00:40:04,668 --> 00:40:06,668
Wow, shut down robot.

751
00:40:11,059 --> 00:40:12,059
What do we do now?

752
00:40:16,771 --> 00:40:18,238
Madam, what are you going to do?

753
00:40:18,238 --> 00:40:19,510
We have to run.

754
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:21,510
Hey, where are you running to?

755
00:40:22,737 --> 00:40:24,005
We need to regroup.

756
00:40:24,005 --> 00:40:26,756
Those two, they already know it’s our plan.

757
00:40:26,756 --> 00:40:27,756
How about Madame Manfah?

758
00:40:27,824 --> 00:40:29,824
Leave her here. Come on, hurry.

759
00:40:30,095 --> 00:40:31,095
Yes, Madam.

760
00:40:43,522 --> 00:40:44,870
You’re here so early.

761
00:40:44,870 --> 00:40:47,854
Well, it’s Buddhist holy day, so I came sit on the Shaman.

762
00:40:47,854 --> 00:40:50,840
Wait, meditate with the Shaman.

763
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:56,840
Good. Meditation will help you find your focus.

764
00:40:59,875 --> 00:41:02,942
Hey, what are you two doing here?

765
00:41:02,942 --> 00:41:06,008
We came to meditate with the Shaman.

766
00:41:06,008 --> 00:41:08,879
And you had to dress all in white like that?

767
00:41:08,879 --> 00:41:11,824
Damn, Tid-Gift, you dare talk about us?

768
00:41:11,824 --> 00:41:13,615
Your outfit is way fancier.

769
00:41:13,615 --> 00:41:15,290
Why didn’t you shave your head too?

770
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,290
Alright, alright.

771
00:41:17,596 --> 00:41:19,591
Since everyone is here,

772
00:41:19,591 --> 00:41:22,591
let’s meditate together.
Begin.

773
00:41:30,778 --> 00:41:31,778
Hey, Sky!

774
00:41:34,843 --> 00:41:37,234
Shaman, Sky is possessed!

775
00:41:37,234 --> 00:41:38,234
I’m not Sky.

776
00:41:38,742 --> 00:41:42,772
In this case, maybe the Shaman should kiss her,
a deep passionate kiss, tongue and all,

777
00:41:42,772 --> 00:41:44,772
so the ghost gets scared and leaves.

778
00:41:45,241 --> 00:41:48,467
No need for the Shaman.
My hands are enough.

779
00:41:48,467 --> 00:41:50,467
Come on, if it won’t leave,
I’ll slap it out.

780
00:41:55,773 --> 00:41:56,773
I won’t leave!

781
00:42:01,125 --> 00:42:02,125
It left.

782
00:42:02,672 --> 00:42:05,057
Damn, you slapped me so hard, bitch.

783
00:42:05,057 --> 00:42:06,057
That hurts.

784
00:42:07,288 --> 00:42:08,288
Alright, alright.

785
00:42:08,602 --> 00:42:12,192
I know you’re all shaken up from being cursed.

786
00:42:12,192 --> 00:42:14,701
So today I have sacred talismans

787
00:42:14,701 --> 00:42:15,893
for you to buy.

788
00:42:15,893 --> 00:42:18,845
Oh, and if we buy enough,

789
00:42:18,845 --> 00:42:21,231
do we get like a meet-and-greet with the Shaman too?

790
00:42:21,231 --> 00:42:23,715
Mhm, 200 baht each.

791
00:42:23,715 --> 00:42:27,024
If you buy ten, I’ll take you on a trip.

792
00:42:27,024 --> 00:42:29,291
Ooh, then I’ll buy them all!

793
00:42:29,291 --> 00:42:32,001
I’ll take them all too! How much?

794
00:42:32,001 --> 00:42:33,269
200 each.

795
00:42:33,269 --> 00:42:35,298
I’ll pay 5,000!

796
00:42:35,298 --> 00:42:38,087
I’ll pay 5,005!

797
00:42:38,087 --> 00:42:40,082
Then I’ll pay 6,000!

798
00:42:40,082 --> 00:42:42,758
I’ll pay 6,006!

